aweme_list.desc: @supercarblondie The idea behind the Bugatti Chiron Tourbillon is to offer @bugatti Chiron owners the opportunity to wear a timepiece that matches their supercar. But set with so many baguette-cut diamonds, it becomes so lavish not even Bugatti can match its light. An accomplishment of watchmaking, gemsetting and design that relies on advanced engineering. Everything in the Jacob & Co. Bugatti Chiron 16 Cylinder Tourbillon is designed to honor the Chiron in a timepiece. Engine block automaton inspired by the Bugatti W16 engine. Its 16 pistons are activated by a genuine crankshaft. The movement is regulated by a rare type of tourbillon : flying and inclined. #jacobandco #inspiredbytheimpossible #supercarblondie #custom #customgift
